notes ""
{
NPCText "Salutations <PC>. Iĺve nearly completed my examination of the autodoc. Just a moment. *time-lapse* How may I be of service to you?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hello Davis. I have been chosen to leave the vault and look for a way to fix the reactor. " linkto "A"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh sorry, wrong turn." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I go fix metal men." linkto "2"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Where I?" linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Is the OS on the autodoc malfunctioning as well?" linkto "1sci" conditions { CHECK_SKILL science >= 50 } notes ""
              }
}
Node "A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "You have been confirmed as the one to go outside the vault?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yes. In fact I probably should get going." linkto "B"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yes. Though I am a little nervous about it." linkto "C"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "B"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Before you go, <PC>, while on the surface could you obtain for me some examples of the outsideĺs Flora and Fauna? Just to placate my curiosity."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Of course I could do that, Davis" linkto "D"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I need to focus on my objective and return as quickly as I can. " linkto "E"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "C"
notes ""
{
NPCText "There is no reason for apprehension. The radiation depleted a half-century ago, if not before that."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Really?" linkto "F"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yeah. I guess you are right. " linkto "F"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Iĺm still not sure itĺs safe. " linkto "F"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "D"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Thank you <PC>. Iĺll be awaiting your return."
      options {
          int=1 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[End]" linkto "done"  notes "new quest added"
              }
}
Node "E"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Do no fret about it then."
      options {
