Node "1sci"
notes ""
{
NPCText "The system wasn't originally intended for the vault inhabitants to remain inside for so long so the time in the bios needed to be reset. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wouldnĺt resetting the clocks make the date inaccurate?" linkto "2sci"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That makes sense. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "2sci"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Actually the calendars repeat every 27 years so as long as everyone keeps that year in mind the dates will be exact."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well at least their was an easy solution. " linkto "3sci"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That is fortunate, but I need to be going now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "2"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Oh i see. You must be special to have been chosen out of all the residents."
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Me Special?" linkto "3"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I need go now." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "3sci"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Speaking of solutions, I hear you were chosen to go look for a way to fix the Mr. Handy robots.  I was curious if while you were out you could retrieve some examples of the flora and fauna that survived the war."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I think I can find something for you, Davis." linkto "done"  notes "new quest"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I will probably be a little busy for that." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "3"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Yes. In fact I have a special assignment for you. Do you think while you are outside you can get an animal or a plant and bring it back to me?"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I do for you" linkto "done"  notes "new quest"
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I don't think I can." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
